NK045(bi)003:1: // yon tan rin po che sdud pa'i bsdus don dri
NK045(bi)003:2: med nor bu'i phreng ba zhes bya ba bzhugs so
NK045(bi)003:3: // bla ma dang rje btsun 'jam pa'i dbyangs la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK045(bi)003:4: de la 'dir dus gsum gyi rgyal ba thams cad
NK045(bi)003:5: kyi gsung chos kyi mdzod mi zad pa thams cad
NK045(bi)003:6: kyi nang na snying po dang mthar thug par 'gyur
NK045(bi)003:7: ba 'phags pa shes rab kyi pha rol tu phyin
NK045(bi)003:8: pa thams cad kyi don yongs su rdzogs par 'dus
NK045(bi)003:9: shing yon tan gyi khyad par du mas 'phags pa
NK045(bi)003:10: yon tan rin po che sdud pa 'di 'chad pa
NK045(bi)003:11: la / dngos bstan stong nyid kyi tshul ltar bshad pa dang /
NK045(bi)003:12: shugs bstan lam gyi mngon rtogs ltar bshad pa gnyis las /
NK045(bi)003:23: mtshams sbyar ba gleng gzhi'i tshigs dang /
NK045(bi)003:26: de nas yang bcom ldan 'das sogs /
NK045(bi)003:28: chos la nyan par bskul ba dang /
NK045(bi)003:29: bstan pa chos kyi rang bzhin /
NK045(bi)003:33: zhar byung chos bstan pa sangs rgyas kyi phrin las su bstan pa gnyis las /
NK045(bi)003:38: dpe don rgyu mtshan gsum re re bzhin /
NK045(bi)003:39: 'dzam bu'i gling 'dir sogs tshigs bcad re res bstan /
NK045(bi)003:40: gnyis pa bstan pa chos kyi rang bzhin la bsgrub bya'i lam dang /
NK045(bi)003:43: lam gyi gtso bo shes rab phar phyin bshad pa dang /
NK045(bi)003:45: dang po la bsdus te bstan pa'i sgo dang /
NK045(bi)003:47: rgyas par bstan pa'i sgo dang gsum /
NK045(bi)003:48: dang po la rten chos 'bras bu rgyas par bshad pa dang /
NK045(bi)003:49: de dag gi skabs bsdu ba gnyis /
NK045(bi)003:57: byang sems kyi sgra don gsum /
NK045(bi)003:61: 'bras bu mtha' gnyis su mi gnas pa'i tshul gsum /
NK045(bi)003:65: gang la shes rab sogs tshigs bcad gcig /
NK045(bi)003:67: shes bya'i yul mi dmigs pa dang /
NK045(bi)003:68: yul can shes rab mi dmigs pa gnyis /
NK045(bi)003:73: gzugs med sogs tshigs bcad gcig /
NK045(bi)003:75: ji ltar kun tu rgyu sogs tshigs bcad gcig /
NK045(bi)003:77: sgrub phyogs nas bstan pa dang /
NK045(bi)003:79: de'i don bsdu ba dang gsum 'di rtsa ba'i sa bcad gsum pa dang gcig gam dpyad /
NK045(bi)003:82: yang 'di shes rab sogs tshigs bcad gcig /
NK045(bi)003:84: gal te mi shes sogs rkang pa bzhi /
NK045(bi)003:86: gang zhig gzugs med sogs rkang pa bzhi /
NK045(bi)003:87: gnyis pa lam spyod med ni /
NK045(bi)003:88: byang chub sems gang sogs tshigs bcad gnyis /
NK045(bi)003:92: gang zhig yod pa sogs rkang pa bzhi /
NK045(bi)003:94: gang 'dir phung po sogs rkang pa bzhi /
NK045(bi)003:95: gnyis pa bshes gnyen gyi khyad par la /
NK045(bi)003:96: sgrub pa dang dgag pa gnyis las /
NK045(bi)003:98: dge ba'i bshes dang sogs rkang pa gnyis /
NK045(bi)003:100: gang zhig sogs rkang pa gnyis /
NK045(bi)003:101: gsum pa byang chub sems dpa'i sgra don la /
NK045(bi)003:102: byang chub sems dpa' zhes pa'i sgra don dang /
NK045(bi)003:103: sems dpa' chen po'i sgra don gnyis las /
NK045(bi)003:105: ci phyir 'di ni sogs rkang pa bzhi /
NK045(bi)003:107: sems can rnams kyi mchog tu gyur pa dang /
NK045(bi)003:108: go cha che ba gnyis las /
NK045(bi)003:110: ci phyir 'di ni sogs rkang pa bzhi /
NK045(bi)003:113: go cha'i tshul bshad pa gnyis las /
NK045(bi)003:115: gtong ba che dang sogs rkang pa bzhi /
NK045(bi)003:119: dper na sgyu ma sogs rkang pa bzhi /
NK045(bi)003:121: gzugs dang 'du shes sogs rkang pa bzhi /
NK045(bi)003:122: gnyis pa nyams su blang bya chos la /
NK045(bi)003:123: theg chen gyi ngo bo mdor bstan pa /
NK045(bi)003:124: de'i rang bzhin rgyas par bshad pa gnyis /
NK045(bi)003:125: dang po la tha snyad du sgra don ngo bo byed las kyi sgo nas bshad pa dang /
NK045(bi)003:126: don dam par de dag mi dmigs par bstan pa gnyis /
NK045(bi)003:128: ci phyir 'di ni sogs rkang pa bzhi /
NK045(bi)003:130: gang zhig zhon nas sogs rkang pa bzhi /
NK045(bi)003:132: gang zag dang lam rang bzhin med par bstan pa dang /
NK045(bi)003:133: de yi don bsdu ba gnyis /
NK045(bi)003:135: lam sgrub pa po gang zag mi dmigs par bstan pa dang /
NK045(bi)003:136: lam sher phyin mi dmigs par bstan pa gnyis /
NK045(bi)003:138: byang chub sems dpa' sogs rkang pa bzhi /
NK045(bi)003:143: byang chub sems dpa' mkhas rig sogs rkang pa bzhi /
NK045(bi)003:145: gal te sems can 'du shes sogs rkang pa bzhi /
NK045(bi)003:146: gnyis pa don bsdu ba ni /
NK045(bi)003:147: bdag ci 'dra ba sogs rkang pa bzhi /
NK045(bi)003:149: 'jig rten dag na chos sogs rkang pa bzhi /
NK045(bi)003:150: gnyis pa skabs bsdu ba ni /
NK045(bi)003:151: byang chub sems dpa' gang zhig sogs rkang pa bzhi //
NK045(bi)003:152: gnyis pa 'bring du dbye ba'i sgo la /
NK045(bi)003:153: ji ltar bslab pa'i gnas bstan pa /
NK045(bi)003:154: de ltar bslab pa'i yul can sher phyin nyid ngos bzung ba /
NK045(bi)003:155: de la brten pa'i bsod nams mngon par 'du bya ba /
NK045(bi)003:156: de'i rang bzhin rgyud la bskyed pa'i tshul dang bzhi las /
NK045(bi)003:157: dang po la mi gnas pa'i tshul dang /
NK045(bi)003:158: de la slob pa'i tshul bshad pa gnyis /
NK045(bi)003:160: mi gnas pa'i gnas pa bshad pa dang /
NK045(bi)003:166: khyad gzhi gzugs la sogs pa la mi gnas pa dang /
NK045(bi)003:167: khyad chos mi rtag sogs su mi gnas pa gnyis /
NK045(bi)003:169: gang zhig gzugs la mi gnas sogs /
NK045(bi)003:172: rtag dang mi rtag sogs rkang pa bzhi /
NK045(bi)003:174: ji ltar 'dren pa sogs rkang pa bzhi /
NK045(bi)003:176: gang dag bde gshegs sogs rkang pa bzhi /
NK045(bi)003:177: gnyis pa de la slob tshul la /
NK045(bi)003:182: chos 'chad pa sogs rkang pa bzhi /
NK045(bi)003:184: gang zag bzhi po sogs rkang pa bzhi /
NK045(bi)003:186: 'bras bu dman pa la mi slob pa'i tshul la slob pa dang /
NK045(bi)003:187: chos thams cad la mi slob pa'i tshul la slob pa gnyis /
NK045(bi)003:189: byang chub sems dpa' mkhas rig sogs rkang pa bzhi /
NK045(bi)003:191: gzugs 'phel yongs su sogs rkang pa bzhi /
NK045(bi)003:192: gnyis pa de ltar bslab pa'i yul can shes rab
NK045(bi)003:193: phar phyin ngos bzung ba la gcig dang tha dad
NK045(bi)003:196: bsam gyis mi khyab par bstan pa /
NK045(bi)003:197: gzod nas dag par bstan pa bzhi /
NK045(bi)003:199: gzugs ni shes rab sogs rkang pa bzhi /
NK045(bi)003:201: dmigs pa rnams kyi sogs rkang pa bzhi /
NK045(bi)003:203: 'du shes tshur rol sogs rkang pa bzhi /
NK045(bi)003:205: sems can gyis mtshon pa'i chos kun gzod nas dag pa dngos dang /
NK045(bi)003:206: de ltar rtogs pa'i phan yon gnyis /
NK045(bi)003:208: gal te ston pas sogs rkang pa bzhi /
NK045(bi)003:210: gang tshe nga ni sogs rkang pa bzhi /
NK045(bi)003:211: gsum pa de la brten pa'i bsod nams mngon par 'du bya ba la /
NK045(bi)003:212: rang gis 'chang ba sogs kyi phan yon dang /
NK045(bi)003:213: gzhan la 'chad pa sogs kyi phan yon gnyis /
NK045(bi)003:215: gnod pas mi tshugs pa dang /
NK045(bi)003:216: bsod nams sdud pa gnyis las /
NK045(bi)003:218: shes rab pha rol sogs rkang pa bzhi /
NK045(bi)003:219: gnyis pa la mchod pa'i phan yon dang /
NK045(bi)003:222: la las bde gshegs sogs tshigs bcad gsum /
NK045(bi)003:224: yum la bslab pas srid zhi'i bde ba kun 'byung tshul dang /
NK045(bi)003:225: yum la bslab pas sku gdung sogs mchod pa brnyes tshul /
NK045(bi)003:226: yum la bslab pas dge rtsa gzhan 'das pa'i phar phyin du 'gyur tshul gsum /
NK045(bi)003:227: dang po la don bstan pa dang /
NK045(bi)003:230: zhi ba'i bde ba 'byung ba dang /
NK045(bi)003:231: srid zhi gnyis ka'i bde ba 'byung tshul gnyis /
NK045(bi)003:233: zhi ba tsam gyis bde ba 'byung tshul /
NK045(bi)003:234: zhi ba chen po'i go 'phang dus gsum gyi sangs rgyas 'byung tshul gnyis /
NK045(bi)003:236: rgyal ba'i shes rab sogs rkang pa gnyis /
NK045(bi)003:238: 'das dang da ltar gyi rgyal ba'i yum du gyur tshul dang /
NK045(bi)003:239: ma 'ongs pa'i sangs rgyas kyi yum du 'gyur tshul gnyis /
NK045(bi)003:241: gang dag 'das dang sogs rkang pa gnyis /
NK045(bi)003:243: gang dag phan dang sogs rkang pa gnyis /
NK045(bi)003:245: 'dus byas bde dang sogs rkang pa gnyis /
NK045(bi)003:246: gnyis pa dpe la sa yi dpes yon tan kun bskyed tshul /
NK045(bi)003:247: 'khor bsgyur gyi dpes yon tan kun 'di yi rjes su 'gro tshul gnyis /
NK045(bi)003:249: sa bon btab nas sogs rkang pa bzhi /
NK045(bi)003:251: 'khor los bsgyur rgyal sogs rkang pa bzhi /
NK045(bi)003:253: yum la bslab pas sku gdung sogs mchod pa brnyes tshul la /
NK045(bi)003:255: de'i rgyu mtshan dpe dang bcas te bshad pa gnyis /
NK045(bi)003:257: rgyal bas brgya byin sogs rkang pa bzhi /
NK045(bi)003:259: ci slad ce na sogs tshigs bcad gsum /
NK045(bi)003:260: gsum pa yum la bslab pas dge rtsa gzhan 'das pa'i sher phyin du 'gyur tshul la /
NK045(bi)003:261: sbyin sogs tshul gcig tu byed pa dang /
NK045(bi)003:264: sbyin pa sbyin pa'i sogs rkang pa bzhi /
NK045(bi)003:266: dper na 'dzam bu'i sogs rkang pa brgyad /
NK045(bi)003:267: gnyis pa gzhan la 'chad pa sogs kyi phan yon la /
NK045(bi)003:269: de ltar bshad pa'i phan yon gnyis /
NK045(bi)003:270: dang po la spang bya sher phyin bcos ma 'chad tshul dang /
NK045(bi)003:271: blang bya sher phyin yang dag 'chad tshul gnyis /
NK045(bi)003:273: byang chub sems dpa' gal te sogs rkang pa bzhi /
NK045(bi)003:275: gang la gzugs min sogs rkang pa bzhi /
NK045(bi)003:276: gnyis pa sher phyin yang dag pa bshad pa'i phan yon la /
NK045(bi)003:280: la las gang+g+aa'i sogs rkang pa bzhi /
NK045(bi)003:281: gnyis pa la rgyu mtshan dngos dang /
NK045(bi)003:284: ci phyir zhe na sogs rkang pa bzhi /
NK045(bi)003:285: gnyis pa la myu gu'i dpes mdor bstan pa dang /
NK045(bi)003:286: nyi ma dang klu yi dpes rgyas par bshad pa gnyis /
NK045(bi)003:288: myu gu med par sogs rkang pa bzhi /
NK045(bi)003:290: rjes 'gro'i dpe nyi mas mtshon pa dang /
NK045(bi)003:291: ldog pa'i dpes klu bdag gis mtshon pa gnyis /
NK045(bi)003:293: nyi ma'i dkyil 'khor sogs rkang pa bzhi /
NK045(bi)003:295: dper na ma dros sogs rkang pa brgyad /
NK045(bi)003:296: bzhi pa sher phyin de'i rang bzhin rgyud la bskyed par bya ba la /
NK045(bi)003:297: rjes thob tu bya ba dang /
NK045(bi)003:298: mnyam bzhag tu bsgom pa gnyis /
NK045(bi)003:300: bsod nams spel ba'i rgyu yi rang /
NK045(bi)003:301: chud mi za ba'i rgyu bsngo ba /
NK045(bi)003:302: gong nas gong du 'phel ba'i rgyu mos pa gsum /
NK045(bi)003:304: byang sems kyi yi rang gi phan yon bstan pa dang /
NK045(bi)003:305: yi rang dang bsngo ba'i gzhi thun mong du bstan pa gnyis /
NK045(bi)003:309: 'jig rten 'di na sogs rkang pa bzhi /
NK045(bi)003:311: nyan thos tshogs rnams sogs rkang pa bzhi /
NK045(bi)003:312: gnyis pa yi rang dang bsngo ba'i gzhi ni /
NK045(bi)003:313: 'das dus sngon gyi sogs tshigs bcad gsum /
NK045(bi)003:314: gnyis pa bsngo ba la dngos dang /
NK045(bi)003:315: de ltar bsngosa pa'i phan yon gnyis /
NK045(bi)003:317: don dam mi dmigs pa'i tshul gyis bsngo ba dang /
NK045(bi)003:318: kun rdzob tu sangs rgyas kyi rjes su slob pa'i bsngo ba gnyis /
NK045(bi)003:320: dgag sgrub so sor bshad pa dang /
NK045(bi)003:321: de'i don bsdu dpe dang bcas par bstan pa gnyis /
NK045(bi)003:322: dang po la dgag bya dmigs bcas kyi bsngo ba /
NK045(bi)003:323: bsgrub bya dmigs med kyi bsngo ba gnyis /
NK045(bi)003:325: yongs bsngo gal te sogs rkang pa bzhi /
NK045(bi)003:327: gal te 'di ltar sogs rkang pa bzhi /
NK045(bi)003:328: gnyis pa de gnyis kyi don bsdu ni /
NK045(bi)003:329: gal te mtshan mar sogs rkang pa bzhi /
NK045(bi)003:330: gnyis pa kun rdzob kyi bsngo ba ni /
NK045(bi)003:331: de ltas 'di ltar sogs rkang pa bzhi /
NK045(bi)003:333: de ltar bsngosa pa'i phan yon la dngos dang /
NK045(bi)003:334: de dpe yi sgo nas rgyas par bstan pa gnyis /
NK045(bi)003:336: de ltar bsod nams sogs rkang pa bzhi /
NK045(bi)003:337: gnyis pa la 'bras bu rnam mkhyen thob pa dang /
NK045(bi)003:338: lam phar phyin dag pa thob tshul gnyis /
NK045(bi)003:340: dmigs bu'i dpes phar phyin gzhan rnam mkhyen du 'khrid pa /
NK045(bi)003:341: mig ma bris pa'i dpes phar phyin gzhan tshang yang rnam mkhyen mi thob pa'i tshul gnyis /
NK045(bi)003:343: dmus long dmigs bu sogs rkang pa bzhi /
NK045(bi)003:345: gang tshe shes rab sogs rkang pa bzhi /
NK045(bi)003:347: mi dmigs pas sher phyin gral du tshud pa nam mkha'i dpes bstan pa /
NK045(bi)003:348: de dang bral na lam yongs su mi dag pa'i tshul gnyis /
NK045(bi)003:350: gang tshe 'dus byas sogs rkang pa bzhi /
NK045(bi)003:352: gal te bdag ni sogs rkang pa bzhi /
NK045(bi)003:356: des na yum la dad pas brtson par gdams pa gsum /
NK045(bi)003:358: byang chub sems dpa' sogs rkang pa bzhi /
NK045(bi)003:360: sngon spyad tshe na sogs rkang pa bzhi /
NK045(bi)003:362: de lta bas na sogs rkang pa bzhi /
NK045(bi)003:363: gnyis pa mnyam gzhag tu bsgom tshul la /
NK045(bi)003:364: rnam par dag pa'i ye shes kyi ngo bo /
NK045(bi)003:366: spyod yul rnam pa bzhi las /
NK045(bi)003:368: gzugs kyi dag pa sogs rkang pa bzhi /
NK045(bi)003:371: zhi mthar mi gnas pa dang /
NK045(bi)003:372: srid mthar mi gnas pa'i byed las gnyis /
NK045(bi)003:374: dpa' bo gar spyod sogs rkang pa bzhi /
NK045(bi)003:376: 'gro ba 'di dag sogs rkang pa bzhi /
NK045(bi)003:377: gsum pa mnyam gzhag ye shes de'i spyod yul la /
NK045(bi)003:378: mi spyod pa'i spyod yul bstan pa dang /
NK045(bi)003:379: de ltar spyod pa'i phan yon dpes bshad pa gnyis /
NK045(bi)003:381: spyod pa yongs dag sogs rkang pa bzhi /
NK045(bi)003:383: de ltar spyod pa'i sogs rkang pa bzhi /
NK045(bi)003:384: bzhi pa mnyam bzhag ye shes de'i rnam pa dmigs med bstan pa ni /
NK045(bi)003:385: chos rnams thams cad sogs rkang pa bzhi /
NK045(bi)003:386: gsum pa rgyas par bstan pa'i sgo la /
NK045(bi)003:387: sbyor ba la bslab pa'i rim pa dang /
NK045(bi)003:388: sbyor ba de'i 'bras bu yang dag par 'grub pa'i tshul dang /
NK045(bi)003:389: de la sbyor ba po gang zag bstan pa dang /
NK045(bi)003:390: de ltar 'jug pa'i gang zag gi che ba dang /
NK045(bi)003:391: des bslab bya chos kyi che ba dang lnga las /
NK045(bi)003:393: bsgom bya sbyor ba'i ngo bo /
NK045(bi)003:394: sbyor ba bsgom pa las byung ba'i yon tan /
NK045(bi)003:397: rkyen dge bshes bshad pa dang lnga /
NK045(bi)003:399: rgyal ba la ni sogs rkang pa bzhi /
NK045(bi)003:401: sbyor ba'i rgyu gus pa'i yon tan /
NK045(bi)003:402: sbyor ba las byung ba'i 'bras bu'i yon tan /
NK045(bi)003:403: gnas skabs sbyor ba'i ngo bo'i yon tan gsum /
NK045(bi)003:405: gang zhig chos 'di sogs rkang pa bzhi /
NK045(bi)003:407: bar chad kyis mi tshugs pa'i yon tan /
NK045(bi)003:408: sku gsum thob pa'i yon tan /
NK045(bi)003:410: dgon pa'i lam ni sogs rkang pa brgyad /
NK045(bi)003:412: chos sku thob pa'i yon tan /
NK045(bi)003:413: longs sku thob pa'i yon tan /
NK045(bi)003:414: sprul sku thob pa'i yon tan gsum /
NK045(bi)003:416: mi zhig rgya mtsho'i sogs rkang pa brgyad /
NK045(bi)003:417: gnyis pa longs sku thob tshul ni /
NK045(bi)003:418: dpyid dus bzang la sogs rkang pa bzhi /
NK045(bi)003:421: dper na bud med sogs rkang pa bzhi /
NK045(bi)003:422: gsum pa ngo bo'i yon tan la /
NK045(bi)003:423: 'phel 'grib sogs su mi rtog kyang myang 'das phyogs gcig la mi reg pa dang /
NK045(bi)003:424: rnam par mi rtog kyang 'gro don 'byung ba gnyis /
NK045(bi)003:426: shes rab pha rol sogs rkang pa bzhi /
NK045(bi)003:428: gang zhig 'di spyod sogs rkang pa bzhi /
NK045(bi)003:429: gsum pa sbyor ba'i bar chod du byung pa bstan pa la /
NK045(bi)003:433: smra ba'i zla ba sogs rkang pa bzhi /
NK045(bi)003:437: bar chad kyis tshugs mi tshugs kyi rgyu bstan pa dang gsum /
NK045(bi)003:439: rgyu sbyor ba nyid nyams pa /
NK045(bi)003:440: lam thog chen las nyams pa /
NK045(bi)003:441: rkyen 'chad nyan gyi tshogs pa dang mi ldan pa /
NK045(bi)003:442: des mtshon pa'i skyon gzhan bstan pa dang bzhi /
NK045(bi)003:444: blo gros las su mi rung bas nyams pa dang /
NK045(bi)003:445: yul la the tshom za bas nyams pa gnyis /
NK045(bi)003:447: rgyal ba'i shes rab sogs rkang pa bzhi /
NK045(bi)003:449: 'di bshad tshe na sogs rkang pa bzhi /
NK045(bi)003:450: gnyis pa lam theg chen las nyams pa la /
NK045(bi)003:451: rnam mkhyen gyi rgyu theg chen spang ba dpes bstan pa dang /
NK045(bi)003:452: dman lam tshol ba dpes bstan pa /
NK045(bi)003:453: theg dman las byang chub chen po tshol ba dpes bstan pa gsum las /
NK045(bi)003:455: de ltar mi shes sogs rkang pa gnyis /
NK045(bi)003:457: glang po rnyed nas sogs rkang pa gnyis /
NK045(bi)003:459: dper na la las sogs rkang pa bzhi /
NK045(bi)003:460: gsum pa 'chad nyan gyi tshogs pa dang mi ldan pa la /
NK045(bi)003:464: bsti stang 'dod par sogs rkang pa bzhi /
NK045(bi)003:466: gang dag de yi sogs rkang pa bzhi /
NK045(bi)003:467: bzhi pa des mtshon pa'i skyon gzhan bstan pa ni /
NK045(bi)003:468: de yi tshe na sogs rkang pa bzhi /
NK045(bi)003:469: gnyis pa bdud las 'byung ba'i rgyu mtshan ni /
NK045(bi)003:470: rin chen rin thang sogs rkang pa bzhi /
NK045(bi)003:471: gsum pa bar chad kyis tshugs mi tshugs kyi rgyu bstan pa la /
NK045(bi)003:472: bar chad de gang la 'byung ba'i yul bstan pa /
NK045(bi)003:473: bar chad de las sangs rgyas kyis bsrung ba'i tshul gnyis /
NK045(bi)003:475: theg par gsar du sogs rkang pa gsum /
NK045(bi)003:480: phyogs bcu'i sangs rgyas sogs rkang pa gcig /
NK045(bi)003:482: mi zhig na bar sogs rkang pa bzhi /
NK045(bi)003:483: bzhi pa sbyor ba'i byed las bshad pa la /
NK045(bi)003:484: rang sras bskyed pa'i bya ba byed pa dang /
NK045(bi)003:485: rang sras yon tan la sbyor ba'i bya ba byed pa gnyis /
NK045(bi)003:487: gang dag 'das dang sogs rkang pa gnyis /
NK045(bi)003:489: gzhi 'khor 'das kyi tshul mkhyen pa la sbyor ba dang /
NK045(bi)003:490: 'bras bu rnam mkhyen gyi mdzad pa la sbyor ba /
NK045(bi)003:491: lam mtha' gnyis 'gog pa'i tshul la sbyor ba gsum /
NK045(bi)003:492: dang po la sher phyin la brten nas 'jig rten gyi bden gnyis la mkhas pa dang /
NK045(bi)003:493: de bzhin nyid rtogs pas mtshan thob pa gnyis /
NK045(bi)003:495: 'jig rten ston pa sogs rkang pa drug /
NK045(bi)003:497: mkhas pa 'jig rten sogs rkang pa bzhi /
NK045(bi)003:498: gnyis pa 'bras bu rnam mkhyen la sbyor tshul la /
NK045(bi)003:499: sher phyin la brten nas don gnyis 'grub pa dang /
NK045(bi)003:500: khyad par du gzhan don du chos ston pa'i tshul gnyis /
NK045(bi)003:502: shes rab pha rol sogs rkang pa bzhi /
NK045(bi)003:504: lam min tshar gcod pa dang /
NK045(bi)003:505: lam yang dag ston pa'i tshul gnyis /
NK045(bi)003:507: dper na seng ge sogs rkang pa bzhi /
NK045(bi)003:509: dper na nam mkha' sogs rkang pa bzhi /
NK045(bi)003:510: gsum pa lam mtha' gnyis 'gog pa'i tshul la sbyor ba la /
NK045(bi)003:517: gzugs rnams mi mthong sogs rkang pa bzhi /
NK045(bi)003:519: nam mkha' mthong zhes sogs rkang pa bzhi /
NK045(bi)003:520: gnyis pa lam de'i byed las la /
NK045(bi)003:521: lam 'bras kyi yon tan kun sdud pa dang /
NK045(bi)003:522: lam gol ba las thag bsring tshul gnyis /
NK045(bi)003:524: blon po'i dpes mdzad pa kun byed pa dang /
NK045(bi)003:525: rgyal po'i dpes yon tan kun sdud pa gnyis /
NK045(bi)003:527: gang gis de ltar sogs rkang pa bzhi /
NK045(bi)003:529: rgyal po grong du sogs rkang pa bzhi /
NK045(bi)003:530: gnyis pa lam gol ba las thag bsring tshul la /
NK045(bi)003:533: gang la bde gshegs sogs rkang pa bzhi /
NK045(bi)003:534: gnyis pa tshul de rgyas bshad la /
NK045(bi)003:538: rgas pa'i dpes bstan pa bzhi po re re la'ang dpe don gnyis res bstan te /
NK045(bi)003:540: dper na rgya mtshor sogs rkang pa bcu gnyis /
NK045(bi)003:542: dper na la las sogs rkang pa brgyad /
NK045(bi)003:544: dper na bcos legs sogs rkang pa brgyad /
NK045(bi)003:546: lo brgya nyi shu sogs rkang pa brgyad /
NK045(bi)003:547: lnga pa rkyen dge ba'i bshes gnyen bstan pa la /
NK045(bi)003:548: bsten bya bshes gnyen bsten pa dang /
NK045(bi)003:549: rten pa po slob ma bshad pa gnyis /
NK045(bi)003:551: mtshan nyid ldan pa'i dge ba'i bshes gnyen la brten dgos tshul dang /
NK045(bi)003:552: bshes gnyen des gdams ngag ston tshul gnyis /
NK045(bi)003:553: dang po la dngos dang de ltar brten dgos pa'i rgyu mtshan gnyis /
NK045(bi)003:555: byang chub sems dpa' sogs rkang pa bzhi /
NK045(bi)003:557: ci phyir zhe na sogs rkang pa bzhi /
NK045(bi)003:558: gnyis pa gdams ngag ston tshul la /
NK045(bi)003:559: gdams pa ji ltar ston pa dang /
NK045(bi)003:560: de ltar bstan pa'i basngagasa pa brjod pa gnyis /
NK045(bi)003:562: sbyin dang tshul khrims sogs rkang pa bzhi /
NK045(bi)003:564: de ltar spyod pa sogs rkang pa bzhi /
NK045(bi)003:565: gnyis pa shes rab zab mo nyan pa'i slob ma bshad pa la /
NK045(bi)003:566: zab mo la yid ches pa dang ldan pa'i slob ma bstan pa dang /
NK045(bi)003:567: de lta bu'i yid ches de dka' bar bstan pa gnyis /
NK045(bi)003:568: dang po la blo zab pa'i tshul zab pa de'i yon tan bstan pa gnyis /
NK045(bi)003:570: grag chen ldan rnams sogs rkang pa bzhi /
NK045(bi)003:572: de dag 'di 'dra'i sogs rkang pa bzhi /
NK045(bi)003:573: gnyis pa zab mo de rtog pa dka' ba'i tshul la /
NK045(bi)003:574: spyad bya'i chos zab par bstan pa dang /
NK045(bi)003:575: de ltar zab ba'i rgyu mtshan gnyis /
NK045(bi)003:577: 'dren pa rnams kyi sogs rkang pa bzhi /
NK045(bi)003:579: sems can rnams ni sogs rkang pa bzhi /
NK045(bi)003:580: gnyis pa sbyor ba des 'bras bu yang dag par 'grub pa'i tshul la /
NK045(bi)003:581: thob bya'i 'bras bu ngos bzung ba dang /
NK045(bi)003:582: lam 'di med na de mi thob pa'i tshul gnyis /
NK045(bi)003:587: nam mkha'i khams ni sogs rkang pa bzhi /
NK045(bi)003:589: 'das pa'i de bzhin sogs rkang pa bzhi /
NK045(bi)003:590: gnyis pa lam 'di med na de mi thob pa'i tshul la /
NK045(bi)003:593: bde gshegs byang chub sogs rkang pa bzhi /
NK045(bi)003:595: lam 'di dang bral na mthar 'bras mi 'grub pa'i tshul dang /
NK045(bi)003:596: de ltar shes nas lam 'dir 'jug pa'i tshul gnyis /
NK045(bi)003:600: bya zhig lus che sogs rkang pa bzhi /
NK045(bi)003:602: rgyal ba rnams kyi sogs rkang pa bzhi /
NK045(bi)003:604: sangs rgyas theg pa sogs rkang pa bzhi /
NK045(bi)003:605: rtsa ba'i gsum pa sbyor ba po gang zag bshad
NK045(bi)003:606: pa la zhus pa'i sgo nas mdor bstan pa dang
NK045(bi)003:607: / lan gyis rgyas par bshad pa gnyis /
NK045(bi)003:609: 'jig rten mgon sogs rkang pa bzhi /
NK045(bi)003:611: rtags kyis mtshon pa'i phyir mi ldog pa ngos bzung ba /
NK045(bi)003:612: phyir mi ldog pa de'i spyod pa'i khyad par /
NK045(bi)003:613: phyir ldog dang mi ldog pa'i khyad par bstan pa gsum /
NK045(bi)003:615: tha dad 'du shes bral sogs tshigs bcad drug /
NK045(bi)003:617: don dam pa'i yul can zab mo'i spyod pa dang /
NK045(bi)003:618: kun rdzob pa'i yul can rgya che ba'i spyod pa dang /
NK045(bi)003:619: zung du 'jug pa thabs mkhas kyi spyod pa gsum las /
NK045(bi)003:620: dang po la spyad bya zab mo'i don ngos bzung ba dang /
NK045(bi)003:621: de las ji ltar spyod tshul gnyis /
NK045(bi)003:623: zab mo nyid bshad pa dang /
NK045(bi)003:624: de la spyad pas bsod nams mngon par 'du bya ba gnyis /
NK045(bi)003:626: gzugs dang tshor dang sogs rkang pa bzhi /
NK045(bi)003:628: de la klan ka spang ba gnyis /
NK045(bi)003:629: dang po la mdor bstan rgyas bshad gnyis /
NK045(bi)003:631: byang chub sems dpa' sogs rkang pa bzhi /
NK045(bi)003:633: zab mo de yid la byas pa dang /
NK045(bi)003:635: mnyam rjes su bsgom pa'i phan yon dang /
NK045(bi)003:636: de lta bu'i bsod nams kyang sgyu ma ltar bltas pa'i phan yon bzhi las /
NK045(bi)003:638: dper na 'dod chags sogs rkang pa bzhi /
NK045(bi)003:640: byang chub sems dpa' sogs rkang pa bzhi /
NK045(bi)003:642: byang chub sems dpa' sogs rkang pa bzhi /
NK045(bi)003:644: bsod nams de yang sogs rkang pa bzhi /
NK045(bi)003:645: gnyis pa klan ka spang ba la /
NK045(bi)003:646: don dam par bsod nams kyi 'bras bu 'phel ba
NK045(bi)003:647: dang spang thob med pas sangs rgya ba mi 'thad
NK045(bi)003:649: kun rdzob tu yang sangs rgyas thob pa mi 'thad pa'i klan ka spang ba gnyis /
NK045(bi)003:651: don dam par zad 'phel med pa dang /
NK045(bi)003:652: med kyang kun rdzob tu sangs rgya ba 'thad pa'i tshul gnyis /
NK045(bi)003:654: sangs rgyas kyis bshad sogs rkang pa bzhi /
NK045(bi)003:656: rgyal ba rnams kyi sogs rkang pa bzhi /
NK045(bi)003:657: gnyis pa kun rdzob tu klan ka spang ba la /
NK045(bi)003:658: spang bya spong ba 'thad pa dang /
NK045(bi)003:659: yon tan thob pa 'thad tshul gnyis /
NK045(bi)003:663: 'bru mar snying po sogs rkang pa bzhi /
NK045(bi)003:665: dang po'i sems kyang sogs rkang pa bzhi /
NK045(bi)003:666: gnyis pa yon tan thob tshul la /
NK045(bi)003:667: yon tan thob pa 'thad pa dang /
NK045(bi)003:668: yon tan rdzogs pa 'thad pa gnyis /
NK045(bi)003:671: rten 'brel gyi sgo nas nges par 'thad pa gnyis /
NK045(bi)003:673: sa bon las ni sogs rkang pa bzhi /
NK045(bi)003:675: sa bon rnyed nas sogs rkang pa bzhi /
NK045(bi)003:676: gnyis pa yon tan rdzogs pa 'thad pa ni /
NK045(bi)003:677: chu yi thigs pas sogs rkang pa bzhi /
NK045(bi)003:678: gnyis pa zab mo de la ji ltar spyod tshul la /
NK045(bi)003:680: de yi yon tan bshad pa gnyis /
NK045(bi)003:682: stong pa mtshan med sogs rkang pa bzhi /
NK045(bi)003:684: de ltar spyod pa sogs rkang pa bzhi /
NK045(bi)003:685: gnyis pa kun rdzob kyi yul can rgya che ba zhing sbyong ba'i spyod pa ni /
NK045(bi)003:686: 'jig rten dgon pa'i sogs rkang pa bzhi /
NK045(bi)003:687: gsum pa zung 'jug thabs mkhas kyi spyod pa bstan pa la mdor bstan /
NK045(bi)003:691: byang chub sems dpa' sogs rkang pa bzhi /
NK045(bi)003:693: dpe brgyad kyi tshul gyis bstan te /
NK045(bi)003:694: sgyu ma'i dpes sems can mi 'dor ba /
NK045(bi)003:695: snod kyi dpes smon lam gyi shugs rdzogs pa /
NK045(bi)003:696: bya 'phur ba'i dpes rten med kyang mi ltung ba /
NK045(bi)003:697: mda' 'phang ba'i dpes ma rdzogs par sdo de ba /
NK045(bi)003:698: rdzu 'phrul gyi dpes sdod kyang gzhan don du mi skyo ba /
NK045(bi)003:699: gdugs 'dzin pa'i dpes mthar mi ltung ba /
NK045(bi)003:700: ded dpon gyi dpes rang gzhan gyi phan bde bsgrub pa /
NK045(bi)003:701: tshong pa'i dpes lam la mkhas pa dang brgyad las /
NK045(bi)003:703: dper na skyes bu sogs rkang pa bcu gnyis /
NK045(bi)003:705: mkha' la rlung brten sogs rkang pa brgyad /
NK045(bi)003:707: gang gi tshe na sogs rkang pa brgyad /
NK045(bi)003:709: dper na 'phong bslab sogs rkang pa brgyad /
NK045(bi)003:711: dper na dge slong sogs rkang pa brgyad /
NK045(bi)003:713: dper na mi 'ga' sogs rkang pa brgyad /
NK045(bi)003:715: dper na rin chen sogs rkang pa brgyad /
NK045(bi)003:717: dper na don gnyer sogs rkang pa brgyad /
NK045(bi)003:722: gang tshe 'gro la sogs rkang ba bzhi /
NK045(bi)003:724: dper na sprul pa'i sogs rkang pa bzhi /
NK045(bi)003:725: gsum pa phyir ldog pa dang mi ldog pa'i khyad par la /
NK045(bi)003:728: gal te spyod pa sogs rkang pa bzhi /
NK045(bi)003:730: phyir mi ldog pa'i rtags dang bdud kyis bslus pa'i khyad par gnyis /
NK045(bi)003:732: dgra bcom pa dang sogs rkang pa bcu gnyis /
NK045(bi)003:735: de spong ba'i thabs la brtson par bstan pa gnyis /
NK045(bi)003:736: dang po la yon tan gyis rlom pa'i bdud /
NK045(bi)003:737: ming gi gzhi las 'ong ba'i bdud /
NK045(bi)003:738: dben pas rlom pa'i bdud dang gsum /
NK045(bi)003:740: ci ste de ni sogs rkang pa bzhi /
NK045(bi)003:742: ming gi gzhi las sogs rkang pa brgyad /
NK045(bi)003:747: rab tu dben pa sogs rkang pa bzhi /
NK045(bi)003:749: nang gi dben pa bstan pa dang /
NK045(bi)003:750: dben pa de ma shes pa'i skyon bshad pa gnyis /
NK045(bi)003:752: rtag tu grong dang sogs rkang pa bzhi /
NK045(bi)003:754: nang gi dben pa dang bral ba'i skyon dang /
NK045(bi)003:755: nang gi dben pa can la brnyas pa'i skyon bstan pa gnyis /
NK045(bi)003:757: gang zhig dpag tshad sogs rkang pa bzhi /
NK045(bi)003:760: des na gzhan gyi tshod dpag dka' bar bstan pa gnyis /
NK045(bi)003:762: byang chub sems dpa' sogs rkang pa bzhi /
NK045(bi)003:764: gang zhig grong ngam sogs rkang pa bzhi /
NK045(bi)003:765: gnyis pa bdud kyi las spong ba'i thabs bstan pa la /
NK045(bi)003:768: de lta bas na sogs rkang pa bzhi /
NK045(bi)003:769: gnyis pa la phyi nang gi yongs 'dzin gnyis bshad pa dang /
NK045(bi)003:770: nang gi yongs 'dzin bye brag tu bshad pa gnyis /
NK045(bi)003:772: sangs rgyas byang chub sogs rkang pa bzhi /
NK045(bi)003:774: sher phyin bshes gnyen yin tshul dang /
NK045(bi)003:775: bshes gnyen de ji ltar bsten tshul gnyis /
NK045(bi)003:777: rgyal ba 'das dang sogs rkang pa bzhi /
NK045(bi)003:779: bsten bya sher phyin gyi ngo bo dang /
NK045(bi)003:780: de bsten dgos par gdams pa gnyis /
NK045(bi)003:783: de lta na kun byang du gyur pa mi 'thad pa'i rtsod spang gnyis /
NK045(bi)003:785: ji ltar shes rab sogs rkang pa bzhi /
NK045(bi)003:789: de ltar bstan pa'i mjug bsdu ba gsum /
NK045(bi)003:791: sems can yongs su sogs rkang pa bzhi /
NK045(bi)003:793: dper na dogs pa'i sogs rkang pa bzhi /
NK045(bi)003:795: ji ltar 'dzin pa sogs rkang pa bzhi /
NK045(bi)003:796: gnyis pa sher phyin de bsten dgos par gdams pa la /
NK045(bi)003:797: dgos pa'i sgo nas chos de la brtson par gdams pa dang /
NK045(bi)003:798: dpe'i sgo nas ji ltar brtson par bya ba dang /
NK045(bi)003:799: de ltar brtson par byas pa'i phan yon bstan pa gsum las /
NK045(bi)003:800: dang po la bsod nams chen po bya ba cung zad kyis 'grub pa /
NK045(bi)003:801: 'gro ba kun gyi sbyin gnas su gyur pa /
NK045(bi)003:802: gdul bya la lam ston por gyur pa gsum /
NK045(bi)003:804: 'dzam bu'i gling na sogs rkang pa brgyad /
NK045(bi)003:806: shes rab pha rol sogs rkang pa bzhi /
NK045(bi)003:808: byang chub sems dpa' sogs rkang pa bzhi /
NK045(bi)003:809: gnyis pa dpe'i sgo nas ji ltar brtson par bya ba ni /
NK045(bi)003:810: mi zhig sngon chad sogs rkang pa brgyad /
NK045(bi)003:812: de ltar brtson pa'i phan yon la /
NK045(bi)003:813: bsgrub pa gzhan zil gyis gnon pa /
NK045(bi)003:814: lha mi'i re gnas su gyur pa /
NK045(bi)003:817: de'i dge ba la gzhan gyis yi rang ba'i phan yon dang lnga las /
NK045(bi)003:819: nyi ma sprin dang sogs rkang pa brgyad /
NK045(bi)003:821: dper na rgyal po sogs rkang pa brgyad /
NK045(bi)003:823: bdud rnams skrags par byed pa dang /
NK045(bi)003:824: bdud kyis de la mi tshugs pa'i tshul gnyis /
NK045(bi)003:826: de yi tshe na sogs rkang pa bzhi /
NK045(bi)003:828: glags mi rnyed pa'i tshul dang /
NK045(bi)003:829: zhar la ldog phyogs glags rnyed pa'i rgyu bstan pa gnyis /
NK045(bi)003:831: gang tshe mkhas pa sogs rkang pa bzhi /
NK045(bi)003:833: glags rnyed pa'i rgyu gtso bo rtsod pa yin par bstan pa /
NK045(bi)003:834: nyes pa de las ldang ba'i thabs bstan pa gnyis /
NK045(bi)003:837: bye brag tu lung bstan ma thob pas thob pa'i byang sems la rtsod pa'i nyes dmigs gnyis /
NK045(bi)003:839: gang tshe byang chub sogs rkang pa brgyad /
NK045(bi)003:841: lung bstan ma thob sogs rkang pa bzhi /
NK045(bi)003:842: gnyis pa nyes pa de las ldang ba'i thabs bstan pa la /
NK045(bi)003:843: kun rdzob tu stobs bzhi tshangs pa'i sgo nas bshags pa dang /
NK045(bi)003:844: don dam par mi dmigs par lta bas bshags pa gnyis /
NK045(bi)003:846: sangs rgyas bzod pa'i sogs rkang pa gnyis /
NK045(bi)003:849: de ltar shes pa'i phan yon gnyis /
NK045(bi)003:851: gang zhig slob tshe sogs rkang pa bzhi /
NK045(bi)003:853: byang chub sems dpa' sogs rkang pa brgyad /
NK045(bi)003:854: bzhi pa phar phyin kun sdud pa la phar phyin kun la bslab par 'gyur ba dang /
NK045(bi)003:855: theg pa kun la bslab par 'gyur tshul gnyis /
NK045(bi)003:856: dang po la rtsa bar gyur pa'i dpe dang /
NK045(bi)003:857: snying por gyur pa'i dpe gnyis /
NK045(bi)003:859: shes rab pha rol sogs rkang pa bzhi /
NK045(bi)003:861: dper na srog gi sogs rkang pa bzhi /
NK045(bi)003:862: gnyis pa theg pa kun la bslab par 'gyur ba ni /
NK045(bi)003:863: byang chub sems mkhas sogs rkang pa bzhi lnga pa
NK045(bi)003:864: de'i dge ba la gzhan gyis yi rang ba'i phan
NK045(bi)003:868: mi ldog byang chub sogs rkang pa bzhi /
NK045(bi)003:870: dge ba don gnyer sogs rkang pa bzhi /
NK045(bi)003:871: rnam grangs bzhi pa gang zag gi che ba la /
NK045(bi)003:872: mi rtog pa'i spyod pa thob pa /
NK045(bi)003:873: mi rtog kyang bya ba byed pa mi 'gal ba'i dpe /
NK045(bi)003:874: de ltar rtogs pa thob pa'i yon tan dang gsum /
NK045(bi)003:878: byang chub sems dpa' sogs rkang pa bzhi /
NK045(bi)003:880: nam mkha'i khams ni sogs rkang pa bzhi /
NK045(bi)003:882: sgyu ma'i skyes bu'i dpes yul sems can du mi rtog pa /
NK045(bi)003:883: sprul pa'i dpes byed pa por mi rtog pa /
NK045(bi)003:884: shing mkhan gyi bzo bo'i dpes 'bras bu la mi rtog pa gsum /
NK045(bi)003:886: skye bo'i dbus na sogs rkang pa brgyad /
NK045(bi)003:888: dper na sangs rgyas sogs rkang pa bzhi /
NK045(bi)003:890: shing mkhan bzo bo sogs rkang pa bzhi /
NK045(bi)003:893: bdud pham par byed pa'i yon tan gnyis /
NK045(bi)003:895: de ltar spyod mkhas sogs rkang pa bzhi /
NK045(bi)003:900: gang+g+aa'i klung mnyam sogs rkang pa bzhi /
NK045(bi)003:902: rgyu rnams bzhi yi sogs rkang pa bzhi //
NK045(bi)003:903: rtsa ba'i sa bcad lnga pa spyad bya chos kyi che ba la /
NK045(bi)003:904: 'bras bu bgrod gcig lam du tshud pa dang /
NK045(bi)003:905: lam gnas pa rnams kyi mchog tu gyur pa dang /
NK045(bi)003:906: shes bya bslab pa thams cad kyi mchog yin pa'i che ba bstan pa gsum /
NK045(bi)003:908: de bzhin gshegs yum sogs rkang pa bzhi /
NK045(bi)003:910: byang sems kyi gnas pa sher phyin ngos bzung ba /
NK045(bi)003:911: de nyid gnas pa gzhan kun gyi mchog tu bstan pa gnyis /
NK045(bi)003:913: chos dbyings de bzhin sogs rkang pa brgyad /
NK045(bi)003:915: dgra bcom rnam thar sogs rkang pa bcu gnyis /
NK045(bi)003:917: bslab pa thams cad kyi mchog tu bstan pa la /
NK045(bi)003:918: ngo bo'i sgo nas mchog tu bstan pa dang /
NK045(bi)003:919: 'bras bu mi zad par 'byin pa'i sgo nas mchog tu bstan pa gnyis /
NK045(bi)003:921: bslab pa 'di ni sogs rkang pa bzhi /
NK045(bi)003:927: 'di ni chos gter sogs rkang pa bzhi /
NK045(bi)003:929: phyi yi rten 'brel gyi sgo nas bshad pa dang /
NK045(bi)003:930: nang gi rten 'brel gyi sgo nas bshad pa gnyis /
NK045(bi)003:933: don sher phyin bshad pa gnyis /
NK045(bi)003:935: shing dang 'bras bu sogs rkang pa bzhi /
NK045(bi)003:937: sangs rgyas sras dang sogs rkang pa bzhi /
NK045(bi)003:940: don lugs ldog rnam byang gi rten 'brel gyi tshul gyis bstan pa gnyis /
NK045(bi)003:942: sems can tha ma sogs rkang pa bzhi /
NK045(bi)003:944: ye shes tshul sgo sogs rkang pa bzhi /
NK045(bi)003:945: gsum pa don bsdu ba ni /
NK045(bi)003:946: byang chub sems dpa' sogs rkang pa bzhi /
NK045(bi)003:947: gnyis pa phar phyin gzhan lnga bshad pa la /
NK045(bi)003:954: bsam gtan gyi phar phyin bshad pa la /
NK045(bi)003:955: 'bras bu dman pa'i rten du gyur pa'i bsam gtan la bslab pa dang /
NK045(bi)003:956: bslab kyang rang don du chags pa med pa dang /
NK045(bi)003:957: chags pa med pa'i sgo nas gzhan don du 'jug pa dang /
NK045(bi)003:958: bsam pa'i dbye bas mchog dman du gyur pa'i tshul gyis mjug bsdu ba bzhi /
NK045(bi)003:959: dang po la bsam gtan bzhi la bslab pa dang /
NK045(bi)003:960: gzugs med kyi snyoms 'jug bzhi la bslab pa'o //
NK045(bi)003:962: mthu chen ldan sogs rkang pa bzhi /
NK045(bi)003:964: shes rab mchog thob sogs rkang pa bzhi /
NK045(bi)003:968: 'di ni yon tan sogs rkang pa bzhi /
NK045(bi)003:972: dper na 'dzam gling sogs rkang pa bzhi /
NK045(bi)003:974: de bzhin byang chub sogs rkang pa bzhi /
NK045(bi)003:979: bdag nyid chen po sogs rkang pa bzhi /
NK045(bi)003:983: dper na mi zhig sogs rkang pa bzhi /
NK045(bi)003:985: de bzhin byang chub sogs rkang pa bzhi /
NK045(bi)003:988: blang bya mchog gi tshul gnyis /
NK045(bi)003:990: gal te byang chub sogs rkang pa bzhi /
NK045(bi)003:992: gzhan yang gzugs dang sogs rkang pa bzhi /
NK045(bi)003:994: gzhan don du brtson par gdams pa /
NK045(bi)003:996: 'khor gsum dag pa'i tshul gyis brtson pa gsum /
NK045(bi)003:1000: sems can gang zag sogs rkang pa bzhi /
NK045(bi)003:1002: gnod pa byas kyang de'i don du brtson pa mi 'dor ba dang /
NK045(bi)003:1003: rtag tu gzhan don la brtson pa'i tshul gnyis /
NK045(bi)003:1008: spyo ba byas sam sogs rkang pa bzhi /
NK045(bi)003:1010: de bzhin byang chub sogs rkang pa bzhi /
NK045(bi)003:1012: bdag gi dge ba sogs rkang pa bzhi /
NK045(bi)003:1013: gnyis pa ma zhum pa la /
NK045(bi)003:1016: byang chub sems dpa' sogs rkang pa bzhi /
NK045(bi)003:1018: spang bya dang gnyen po gnyis /
NK045(bi)003:1020: byang chub sems dpa' sogs rkang pa bzhi /
NK045(bi)003:1022: dus kyi dbang du byas pa dang /
NK045(bi)003:1023: dngos po'i dbang du byas pa gnyis /
NK045(bi)003:1025: byang chub mchog tu sogs rkang pa bzhi /
NK045(bi)003:1027: gal te 'ga' zhig sogs rkang pa brgyad /
NK045(bi)003:1032: 'gro ba yongs su sogs rkang pa bzhi /
NK045(bi)003:1034: gang tshe lus dang sogs rkang pa bzhi /
NK045(bi)003:1036: chos la nges sems kyi bzod pa /
NK045(bi)003:1037: gnod pas mi mjed pa'i bzod pa /
NK045(bi)003:1038: sdug bsngal dang len gyi bzod pa gsum /
NK045(bi)003:1043: gal te gzhan las sogs rkang pa bzhi /
NK045(bi)003:1045: byang chub sems dpa' sogs rkang pa brgyad /
NK045(bi)003:1047: gnod pa la ci mi snyam pa'i bzod pa la /
NK045(bi)003:1048: ji ltar bzod par bya ba dang /
NK045(bi)003:1049: de ltar bzod pa'i 'bras bu gnyis /
NK045(bi)003:1052: sems can sogs rkang pa bzhi /
NK045(bi)003:1054: byang chub sems dpa' sogs rkang pa bzhi /
NK045(bi)003:1055: gsum pa sdug bsngal dang len gyi bzod pa bstan pa ni /
NK045(bi)003:1056: bzod byed 'di snyam sogs rkang pa brgyad /
NK045(bi)003:1058: mchog gi tshul khrims dang ldan pa'i phan yon dang /
NK045(bi)003:1059: tshul khrims de'i mchog dman gyi dbye ba bshad pa gnyis /
NK045(bi)003:1061: tshul khrims kyis ni sogs rkang pa bzhi /
NK045(bi)003:1064: kun slong gi sgo nas dang /
NK045(bi)003:1065: rlom pa yod med kyi sgo nas dbye ba dang gsum /
NK045(bi)003:1067: gal te rang rgyal dgra bcom sogs rkang pa bzhi /
NK045(bi)003:1071: chos gang nges pa'i sogs rkang pa bzhi /
NK045(bi)003:1076: gal te byang chub sogs rkang pa bzhi /
NK045(bi)003:1078: gal te bskal pa sogs rkang pa bzhi /
NK045(bi)003:1080: blang bya dang spang bya gnyis /
NK045(bi)003:1082: tshul khrims bsrung zhing sogs rkang pa bzhi /
NK045(bi)003:1085: de'i gnyen po bstan pa gnyis /
NK045(bi)003:1087: gal te byang chub sogs rkang pa bzhi /
NK045(bi)003:1089: gang la bdag gi sogs rkang pa bzhi /
NK045(bi)003:1091: sbyin pa btang ba dang ma btang ba'i skyon yon
NK045(bi)003:1092: shes nas sbyin pa la dga' bar bya ba dang
NK045(bi)003:1093: / tshul ji ltar sbyin pa btang bar bya ba gnyis /
NK045(bi)003:1095: byang chub sems dpas sbyin pa gtong ba'i tshul /
NK045(bi)003:1096: phal pas de ltar ma btang ba'i skyon /
NK045(bi)003:1097: de ltar shes nas sbyin pa la mos par bya ba'i tshul gsum /
NK045(bi)003:1099: sems can dag pa sogs rkang pa brgyad /
NK045(bi)003:1101: bdag tu 'du shes sogs rkang pa bzhi /
NK045(bi)003:1103: de tshe byang chub sogs rkang pa bzhi /
NK045(bi)003:1104: gnyis pa ji ltar gtong tshul la /
NK045(bi)003:1107: dang po la snying rjes gzhan don du gtong ba /
NK045(bi)003:1108: thabs mkhas pas yongs su bsngo ba dang ldan pa /
NK045(bi)003:1109: rnam smin dang dngos po la ma chags par gtong ba gsum /
NK045(bi)003:1111: byang chub sems dpa' sogs rkang pa gsum /
NK045(bi)003:1113: de yang 'gro ba'i sogs rkang pa cig /
NK045(bi)003:1115: sbyin pa byin nas sogs rkang pa gnyis /
NK045(bi)003:1119: de lta gtong la sogs rkang pa gnyis /
NK045(bi)003:1121: snying rje sogs thabs mkhas pa dang ldan pa'i sbyin pa'i phan yon dang /
NK045(bi)003:1122: ma chags par btang ba'i phan yon gnyis /
NK045(bi)003:1124: srid pa gsum na sogs rkang pa bcu gnyis /
NK045(bi)003:1126: gal te byang chub sogs rkang pa bzhi /
NK045(bi)003:1127: gnyis pa lam gyi 'bras bu bshad pa la /
NK045(bi)003:1128: lam bye brag pa'i 'bras bu dang /
NK045(bi)003:1129: lam yongs su rdzogs pa'i 'bras bu gnyis /
NK045(bi)003:1131: byang chub sems dpa'i sbyin pas sogs rkang pa bcu drug /
NK045(bi)003:1133: chos 'di yongs rdzogs byas nas sogs rkang pa bzhi /
NK045(bi)003:1134: gsum pa de ltar bstan pa'i dgos pas mjug bsdu ba ni /
NK045(bi)003:1135: 'gro ba'i nad gso sogs rkang pa bzhi /
NK045(bi)003:1136: bzhi pa mjug gi don la /
NK045(bi)003:1137: gzhung lhag ma ma lus par ston pa'i tshig gis skabs bsdu ba dang /
NK045(bi)003:1138: khungs btsun par ston pa'i ched du lo ts+aa ba'i 'gyur byang smos pa gnyis las /
NK045(bi)003:1140: 'phags pa shes rab kyi sogs dang /
NK045(bi)003:1142: rgya gar gyi mkhan po sogs kyis bstan to //
NK045(bi)003:1143: rtsa ba'i sa bcad gnyis pa lam mngon par rtogs
NK045(bi)003:1144: pa'i rim pa dang sbyar ba ni zur du yod
NK045(bi)003:1146: yon tan rin po che sdud pa'i 'grel pa rgyal
NK045(bi)003:1147: ba'i yum gyi dgongs don la phyin ci ma log
NK045(bi)003:1148: par 'jug pa'i legs bshad ces bya ba mi pham
NK045(bi)003:1149: 'jam dpal dgyes pa'i rdo rje'i gsung las zur du
NK045(bi)003:1152: // dge 'dis deng bzung byang chub mchog gi bar //
NK045(bi)003:1153: mkhyen brtse nus pa'i yon tan gong 'phel zhing //
NK045(bi)003:1154: rigs gsum sems dpa' mchog gi rnam thar bzhin //
NK045(bi)003:1155: rgyal bstan mchog nyid bdag gis 'dzin gyur cig /
NK045(bi)003:1156: mkha' khyab zhing gi yid can ji snyed kun //
NK045(bi)003:1157: bstan dang bstan pa'i snying po'i lam bzang la //
NK045(bi)003:1158: bdag nyid gcig pus legs par bkod gyur nas //
NK045(bi)003:1159: kun kyang kun mkhyen rgyal ba nyid gyur cig /
NK045(bi)003:1160: skad cig tsam yang rang don yid byed blo //
NK045(bi)003:1161: bdag gi rgyud la nam yang mi skye zhing //
NK045(bi)003:1162: zung 'jug thabs mkhas mchog gis mkha' khyab tu //
NK045(bi)003:1163: rgyal ba'i phrin las srid mthar spel gyur cig //
